text.tspan: As a new buyer I want to understand how the application works best so that I can quickly complete my registration
As a new buyer I was to LiveChat with someone from the company so I can have a personal communication before registrating.
As a new buyer I want to register so that I will have a buyer account with st-art to be able to save preferable work, get notification
of new artists or artwork, buy and commissioned artwork
As an artist with an account I want to upload new work for my portfolio to keep my profile up to date
As an artist with an account I want to be able to view my dashboard to make changes in my profile/(Exhibition graph) view history
of event participations and artwork sale.
As an artist with an account I want to search other artists from St-Art according to my preferences using selected filters so that I
will get inspired As an artist with an account I want to exhibit my artwork in st-arts events so I will sell my artwork, expose myself,
promote myself As a artist with an account I want to get updates about st-arts events/new artists/new artwork so I will stay
